snippet.title: The Teletransport Smurf - Full Playthrough
snippet.description: My disc is scratched, but it still works! Unedited, save for 5:27 of course. This was one of my most favourite games when I was younger. This game uses the same intro as the one from the Mega-CD version, though with voices.
